      "value": "<p>You can bludgeon your foes and send them reeling.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Str 13, base attack bonus +4</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you hit with the first attack during a full attack action while wielding a melee weapon that deals bludgeoning damage, you can spend a Resolve Point. If you do, on a hit, your second attack causes your foe to become @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{staggered} for 1 round unless they succeed on a Fortitude Save. The DC is equal to 15 + your base attack bonus.</p>"
